author: Inside Edition
description: Financial Planner Jeff Geraci suffered a widowmaker heart attack at the wheel of his car, then, unconscious, he crashed into an office building. Geraci happened to crash into a cardiologist's office. Cardiologist Dr. Deepak Talreja was in his office in Virginia Beach when he heard the crash. Geraci was revived on the scene and rushed to the hospital. Now the 64-year-old thanks the doctor who was in the right place at the right time.
title: Driver Suffering Heart Attack Crashes Into Cardiologist's Office

author: Inside Edition
description: Dr. Harleen Grewal was speaking at a Republican woman's event in Los Angeles when she joked that she gave Democrats a lesser dose of anesthesia than other patients. She is under fire Friday. Grewal made the remarks last year but the video just resurfaced on social media and reaction has been swift. Grewal has had to hire extra security because she says her staff and patients are being harassed. Meanwhile, Grewal wants people to know she really was just joking.
title: Dentist Under Fire After Joking About Giving Democrats Less Anesthesia

author: Inside Edition
description: Armed with wagons, these ladies raced to find the best deals on toys, school supplies, kids clothing, books, and baby gear. More than 500,000 items are for sale inside a 70,000-square-foot expo center outside Philadelphia. Tracy Panase is the CEO of "Just Between Friends" which originally started in 1997 as a sale in one mom's living room. Now, it’s a $53 million business with 150 stores across 33 states. Check out this link to find a sale near you: https://www.jbfsale.com/
title: 'Just Between Friends' Helps Parents Buy Affordable Items For Kids

author: Inside Edition
description: Polar bears have taken over a tiny town on an island in the Chukchi Sea, on the far east coast of Russia. To be fair to the bears, they didn't evict anyone. These houses were abandoned. They used to be occupied by workers at a now defunct polar research station that shuttered in 1992. Inside Edition Digital’s Mara Montalbano has more.
title: Polar Bears Move Into Houses In Abandoned Research Town In Russia

author: Inside Edition
description: The Trump attorney who indicted former FBI director Jim Comey is under fire Friday. Lindsey Halligan, who was appointed Monday, delivered what President Donald Trump wanted: Comey's indictment. As he headed to a golf tournament, Trump brushed off the criticism that he is on a revenge crusade. Newly appointed US Attorney Halligan has never prosecuted a case. The 36-year-old is a former insurance lawyer. She met Trump at his Palm Beach golf club and joined his legal team.
title: US Attorney Lindsey Halligan Had Never Prosecuted Case Before Comey

author: Inside Edition
description: Just another day in Florida as an alligator turned up on someone's front porch. So that means there was a call made to the local sheriff's office to have the trespasser removed. Two Lake County Sheriff's deputies showed up to the home in Clermont. They also had a drone keeping tabs on the action from above. The gator first tried to give them the slip by going around the house and into the backyard. Inside Edition Digital’s Mara Montalbano has more.
title: Deputy Uses Lasso To Remove Alligator From Backyard In Florida

author: Inside Edition
description: According to the New York Post, Kate Gosselin is now living with her former bodyguard, Steve Neild.
title: Kate Gosselin Reveals Relationship With Bodyguard #shorts
